DESKTOP CALL RECORDER - LICENSE & ATTRIBUTION
========================================

The following software is a high-fidelity reconstruction and divergent evolution 
of the original "google-voice-desktop-app" by Jerrod Lankford. 

This version has been entirely re-architected for high-fidelity isolation 
(WASAPI recording, Parakeet V3 ONNX transcription, and Llama-cpp summarization).

